{"sections":[],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/mapsndk\/updatesdk"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"text":"Overview","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"MapsNDK позволяет получить вам совершенно новый опыт работы с картографической информацией в ваших приложениях в сравнении с JS MapsSDK. В этом руководстве будет описан процесс перехода с прошлой версии на новую."}]},{"text":"Установка MapsNDK","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"%D0%A3%D1%81%D1%82%D0%B0%D0%BD%D0%BE%D0%B2%D0%BA%D0%B0-MapsNDK"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"MapsNDK является не обновлением для JS MapsSDK, а полноценной новой библиотекой, поэтому вы не сможете совершить переход с помощью обновления пакета в SPM, пода в CocoaPods. Вам необходимо произвести установку MapsNDK одним из способов, описанных в статье "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNDK\/documentation\/MapsNDK\/StartUsing"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"text":"Переход на MapsNDK","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"%D0%9F%D0%B5%D1%80%D0%B5%D1%85%D0%BE%D0%B4-%D0%BD%D0%B0-MapsNDK"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Для осуществления перехода на новую версию SDK сделайте следующий шаги:","type":"text"}]},{"text":"Шаг 1. Конфигурирование SDK","type":"heading","level":3,"anchor":"%D0%A8%D0%B0%D0%B3-1-%D0%9A%D0%BE%D0%BD%D1%84%D0%B8%D0%B3%D1%83%D1%80%D0%B8%D1%80%D0%BE%D0%B2%D0%B0%D0%BD%D0%B8%D0%B5-SDK"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"MapsNDK требует произвести конфигурирование SDK до создания первого экземпляра "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"MapView"},{"type":"text","text":". Для конфигурирования служит метод "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"MapsNDKConfigurator\/setup(baseURL:apiKey:diskCachePath:maxCacheSizeBytes:fileTimeoutSec:)"},{"type":"text","text":". Подробнее о его использовании можно прочитать в статье "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNDK\/documentation\/MapsNDK\/StartUsing","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["\/\/ БЫЛО","\/\/ Предварительное конфигурирование SDK не требовалось","","\/\/ СТАЛО","MapsNDKConfigurator.setup(apiKey: ##API-ключ##)"]},{"text":"Шаг 2. Конфигурирование MapView","type":"heading","level":3,"anchor":"%D0%A8%D0%B0%D0%B3-2-%D0%9A%D0%BE%D0%BD%D1%84%D0%B8%D0%B3%D1%83%D1%80%D0%B8%D1%80%D0%BE%D0%B2%D0%B0%D0%BD%D0%B8%D0%B5-MapView"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Теперь конфигурацию карты (стартовое положение камеры, стартовый стиль), а так же делегат необходимо передавать в инициализатор объекта "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"MapView"},{"type":"text","text":" ("},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNDK\/documentation\/MapsNDK\/MapView\/init(frame:configuration:delegate:)","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":")."}]},{"code":["\/\/ БЫЛО","\/\/ Создаем объект карты","let mapView = MapView()","\/\/ Создаем объект конфигурации","let mapConfig = MapViewConfig(","    apiKey: \"##API_KEY##\",","    center: Coordinates(lng: 33, lat: 55),","    zoomLevel: 11,","    style: .automatic",")","\/\/ Устанавливаем конфигурацию","mapView.setup(mapConfig)","\/\/ Устанавливаем делегат","mapView.delegate = self","","\/\/ СТАЛО","let configuration = MapConfiguration(","    center: Coordinates(","        lng: 35.910974,","        lat: 56.859207","    ),","    zoom: 15,","    predefinedStyle: style,","    selectFeatures: .all,","    cameraMode: .earth",")","\/\/ Передаем конфигурацию и позже отдельно устанавливаем делегат","mapView = MapView(configuration: configuration)","mapView.delegate = self","","\/\/ ИЛИ","\/\/ Передаем конфигурацию и делегат одновременно","mapView = MapView(configuration: configuration, delegate: self)"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"text":"Шаг 3. Изменение методов перемещение камеры","anchor":"%D0%A8%D0%B0%D0%B3-3-%D0%98%D0%B7%D0%BC%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%B8%D0%B5-%D0%BC%D0%B5%D1%82%D0%BE%D0%B4%D0%BE%D0%B2-%D0%BF%D0%B5%D1%80%D0%B5%D0%BC%D0%B5%D1%89%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%B8%D0%B5-%D0%BA%D0%B0%D0%BC%D0%B5%D1%80%D1%8B","level":3,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Для перемещения камеры теперь необходимо обращаться к контроллеру "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNDK\/documentation\/MapsNDK\/CameraController"},{"type":"text","text":" через свойство "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNDK\/documentation\/MapsNDK\/MapView\/camera"},{"type":"text","text":". Ранее методы управления находились непосредственно в API класса "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"MapView"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Для перемещения камеры используется методы группы ","type":"text"},{"code":"flyTo","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" и другие. Подробнее об это читайте в статье ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNDK\/documentation\/MapsNDK\/CameraMoving"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["\/\/ БЫЛО","mapView.flyTo(Coordinates(lng: 33, lat: 55), animated: true, duration: 2)","","\/\/ СТАЛО","mapView.camera.flyTo(coordinates: .center(Coordinates(lng: 37.427278, lat: 55.756486)), ","                        cameraOptions: .init(bearing: 80, zoom: 12, pitch: 0), ","                        animationOptions: .init(easing: .easeInOut, duration: .max(value: 2)))"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"text":"Шаг 4. Изменение методов управления индикатором пользователя","anchor":"%D0%A8%D0%B0%D0%B3-4-%D0%98%D0%B7%D0%BC%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%B8%D0%B5-%D0%BC%D0%B5%D1%82%D0%BE%D0%B4%D0%BE%D0%B2-%D1%83%D0%BF%D1%80%D0%B0%D0%B2%D0%BB%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%B8%D1%8F-%D0%B8%D0%BD%D0%B4%D0%B8%D0%BA%D0%B0%D1%82%D0%BE%D1%80%D0%BE%D0%BC-%D0%BF%D0%BE%D0%BB%D1%8C%D0%B7%D0%BE%D0%B2%D0%B0%D1%82%D0%B5%D0%BB%D1%8F","level":3,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Для управления индикатором пользователя на карте необходимо обращаться к контроллеру ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNDK\/documentation\/MapsNDK\/UserPointerController","type":"reference"},{"text":" через свойство ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNDK\/documentation\/MapsNDK\/MapView\/userPointer","type":"reference"},{"text":". Ранее методы управления находились непосредственно в API класса ","type":"text"},{"code":"MapView","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Для отображения и перемещения индикатора пользователя используется группа методов "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"setCurrentLocation"},{"type":"text","text":". Подробнее об это читайте в статье "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNDK\/documentation\/MapsNDK\/UserPointer"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["\/\/ БЫЛО","mapView.setCurrentLocation(Coordinates(lng: 33, lat: 55), bearing: 0, accuracy: 0)","","\/\/ СТАЛО","mapView.userPointer.setCurrentLocation(","    coordinates: Coordinates(lng: 33, lat: 55),","    bearing: 0,","    accuracy: 0,","    animationDuration: 1)"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"text":"Шаг 5. Изменение логики обработки событий карты","anchor":"%D0%A8%D0%B0%D0%B3-5-%D0%98%D0%B7%D0%BC%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%B8%D0%B5-%D0%BB%D0%BE%D0%B3%D0%B8%D0%BA%D0%B8-%D0%BE%D0%B1%D1%80%D0%B0%D0%B1%D0%BE%D1%82%D0%BA%D0%B8-%D1%81%D0%BE%D0%B1%D1%8B%D1%82%D0%B8%D0%B9-%D0%BA%D0%B0%D1%80%D1%82%D1%8B","level":3,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"В MapsNDK сильно переработана система событий, они стали более логичными. Теперь практически для всех типов событий (перемещение камеры, клики по маркерам, события жизненного цикла карты) используется метод ","type":"text"},{"code":"MapViewDelegate\/mapView(_:didReceiveEvent:)-7k969","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Более подробно об обработке событий читайте в статье ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNDK\/documentation\/MapsNDK\/Lifecycle","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Пример отслеживания событий нажатия на маркер"}]}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["\/\/ БЫЛО","class MapDelegate: MapViewDelegate{","    func mapView(_ map: MapView, didSelectMarkerID markerID: String) {}","    func mapView(_ map: MapView, didReceiveEvent event: String) {","            \/\/ ...","            \/\/ event.type = .clickOnMarker","            \/\/ ...","        }","}","","\/\/ СТАЛО","class MapDelegate: MapViewDelegate{","    func mapView(_ map: MapView, didReceiveEvent event: MapEvent) {","        switch event {","            \/\/ ...","            \/\/ event.type = .platformMarkerDidSelect","            \/\/ или","            \/\/ event.type = .markerDidSelect","            \/\/ ...","        }","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"style":"warning","type":"aside","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"В данный момент MapsNDK имеет две реализации функционала маркеров: ","type":"text"},{"code":"PlatformMarker","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" и ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNDK\/documentation\/MapsNDK\/Marker","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":". В дальнейшем этот API будет отмечен, как устаревший, его заменит единая более совершенная реализация маркеров.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"Warning"},{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Пример отслеживания событий перемещения камеры"}],"type":"strong"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["\/\/ БЫЛО","class MapDelegate: MapViewDelegate{","    func mapView(_: MapView, didMoveCenterToCoords coords: Coordinates, zoom: Double, bounds: MapBounds) {}","    func mapView(_: MapView, didChangeZoom zoom: Double, scale: Double) {}","}","","\/\/ СТАЛО","class MapDelegate: MapViewDelegate{","    func mapView(_ map: MapView, didReceiveEvent event: MapEvent) {","        switch event {","            \/\/ ...","            \/\/ event.type = .cameraDidMove","            \/\/ ...","        }","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Пример отслеживания событий загрузки карты"}],"type":"strong"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["\/\/ БЫЛО","class MapDelegate: MapViewDelegate{","    func mapViewDidLoad(_: MapView) {","        \/\/ ...","    }","}","","\/\/ СТАЛО","class MapDelegate: MapViewDelegate{","    func mapView(_ map: MapView, didReceiveEvent event: MapEvent) {","        switch event {","            \/\/ ...","            \/\/ event.type = .mapDidShow","            \/\/ ...","        }","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Пример отслеживания событий тапа по карте","type":"text"}]}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["\/\/ БЫЛО","class MapDelegate: MapViewDelegate{","    func mapView(_: MapView, didTapCoords coords: Coordinates, uiCoords: CGPoint) {}","    func mapView(_: MapView, didLongTapCoords coords: Coordinates, uiCoords: CGPoint) {}","}","","\/\/ СТАЛО","class MapDelegate: MapViewDelegate{","    func mapView(_ map: MapView, didReceiveEvent event: MapEvent) {","        switch event {","            \/\/ ...","            \/\/ event.type = .tap","            \/\/ или","            \/\/ event.type = .longTap","            \/\/ ...","        }","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Пример отслеживания событий смены режима следования","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["\/\/ БЫЛО","class MapDelegate: MapViewDelegate{","    func mapView(_: MapView, didChangeMode mode: MapMode) {}","}","","\/\/ СТАЛО","class MapDelegate: MapViewDelegate{","    func mapView(_: MapView, willChangeModeTo nextMode: MapMode) -> MapMode {}","    func mapView(_: MapView, didChangeModeTo mode: MapMode) {}","}"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Пример отслеживания событий использования контролов (кнопок управления)"}]}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["\/\/ БЫЛО","class MapDelegate: MapViewDelegate{","    func mapView(_: MapView, didReceiveControlEvent _: MapControlEvent) {}","}","","\/\/ СТАЛО","class MapDelegate: MapViewDelegate{","    func mapView(_ map: MapView, didReceiveEvent event: MapEvent) {","        switch event {","            \/\/ ...","            \/\/ event.type = .cameraDidMove(_, reason, _) с параметром reason = .control","            \/\/ ...","        }","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"}],"kind":"content"}],"abstract":[{"text":"Сделайте переход со старого JS MapsSDK на MapsNDK максимально просто.","type":"text"}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/MapsNDK\/documentation\/MapsNDK\/UpdateSdk"},"kind":"article","metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"MapsNDK"}],"roleHeading":"Article","title":"Переход с JS MapsSDK","role":"article"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/MapsNDK\/documentation\/MapsNDK"]]},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"references":{"doc://MapsNDK/documentation/MapsNDK/UserPointerController":{"url":"\/documentation\/mapsndk\/userpointercontroller","identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNDK\/documentation\/MapsNDK\/UserPointerController","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"UserPointerController"}],"type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"UserPointerController"}],"title":"UserPointerController","abstract":[],"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol"},"doc://MapsNDK/documentation/MapsNDK/MapView/camera":{"title":"camera","identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNDK\/documentation\/MapsNDK\/MapView\/camera","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text